{"tid":1467770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求軍師］阻你2分鐘 運動勝與負","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T21:29:30.000Z","uid":94798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fbf3ad4f8a281915aa333550b33f6da99b6890b5","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:17.000Z","msg":"相信經過今日機場<br />\n大家都會覺得我地輸哂<br />\n<br />\n其實大家真係要諗一諗<br />\n自從「二哥」回歸之後<br />\n我地既運動 開始出現左問題<br />\n自從 11/8 有鬼捉手足<br />\n12、13/8 我見到既係大家開始意見不一致<br />\n為左捉鬼而搞到大家會開始屌 開始分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家既情況就好似當年14年雨傘運動咁<br />\n分化下就會自亂陣腳<br />\n我地抗爭既目標就會因為正中佢地下懷而收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係前線做任何事都會諗住咪鬼就推唔郁個運動<br />\n捉到鬼係好事 但比你捉多10個又如何<br />\n會focus左變成<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">捉鬼遊戲</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日我地都有做錯，但我地都做靠改善、進步好中先行到呢一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">六個條命，700個義士<br />\n仲有好多手足因為滅火而敏感、傷哂<br />\n有好多捐物資而冇錢開飯</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地絕對唔可以比佢地犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要靠大家團結先走埋一齊<br />\n先可以贏依場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以比人睇死做曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記住 今次輸左 香港就會永久玩撚完<br />\n要贏 一定要靠大家<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">要做個有智有勇有謀既香港人！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要每一日都要傾 都要檢討<br />\n<br />\n和理非有和理非既諗法<br />\n勇武有勇武既諗法<br />\n我地唔傾唔講 只會同共狗冇分別<br />\n<br />\n黎緊機場繼唔繼續唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n而家最緊要係18/8 民陣大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u29eptv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu29eptv.jpg&h=c56d882d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">煞停警黑暴力  落實五大訴求</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">8月18日（日）<br />\n下午2時30分<br />\n維園集合往遮打道 終點集會<br />\n不反對通知書申請中</span><br />\n<br />\n而靠大家幫手做宣傳<br />\n要搵哂所有和理非、勇武、銀髮族等等<br />\n希望要話到比全世界聽 <br />\n我地既訴求<br />\n仍然都係未答覆過！<br />\n<br />\n預左好多負皮<br />\n皆因P牌仔<br />\n<br />\n最後再講多次 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>每日一定要檢討賽果</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n兄弟爬山，一齊努力。<br />\n一個都不能少！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"027f7ed690b8afb9d7c9f5ee5645b1f899d9f2a7","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186c37731363f717bdef1b2b944e0361b574a30c","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:32.000Z","msg":"檢討賽果真係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa57637982a27b59ff26822f5772aed3b4fd6350","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f25fa6a197eaa1288752f06b670bddc673c638b7","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e12429cf1d27986382d2cee1f2515afbfddab5f1","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3dd2d223984e1ed84979e4449fd0c40db75cd3d","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc02629ba9db29ab9721d5287f321fa7851ba870","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee4e142eeab8b42b932ad61e0e13471f2b186eb0","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:47.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"cfcb769d07f03604c758684590c4776043061899","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:12.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"0223a79a95aa2a3f8e85a87c16916c4f78ae5ccf","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:29:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6091eefd35666ae8fbf37ff8d80ec7a36fa02b4","tid":1467770,"uid":94798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:29:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}